INSERT INTO `rental` VALUES (1,1855,'Seabreeze Apartments by Taprobane',NULL,'Seabreeze Resorts by Taprobane is located in a prime area of of Negombo close to the beach,restaurants & all other local amenities.\nThis is an ideal place for a family of 6 or even young couples looking for a romantic getaway.\nIf you are a couple looking to book one room at the property please contact Manager for a special quote.\nThe owner of the property, Mrs. Pushpa Fernando is a British citizen and is always keen in doing the best for her guests at all times.\nThere is staff appointed for the maintenance of the property and for the benefit of guests.\nYou can rest be assured that you will enjoy your stay at Seabreeze Resorts by Taprobane no matter which time of the year you arrive as you will be well looked after by our experienced staff at all times..\n\nTourist License / Licencia de turis...More','$70','3 bedrooms','3 bathrooms','6 guests','2 nights minimum','Nishantha W',NULL,NULL,'7.23198','79.84305','https://www.tripadvisor.com//VacationRentalReview-g12549255-d24807213-Seabreeze_Apartments_by_Taprobane-Ettukala_Negombo_Western_Province.html'),(2,525,'Jude\'s Home',NULL,'About this listing\n\nChill at this waterfront home near Negombo. The price is for a double, non-A/C room. There are four rooms available, one of which has A/C.\n\nThe Space\n\nJude\'s is a newly built, colorful building right in from of Kochchikade\'s traditional catamaran harbor. It has four rooms on two floors. The upper rooms have a balcony, while the lower floors have a veranda. There\'s a nice outside area, wifi and parking available. And a friendly dog called Browny.\n\nInteraction with Guests\n\nYour host, Jude, is a middle aged married man, who runs the place with his youngest son Nipun. His other two sons live in Australia. The home was bought with the savings of his career as a fisherman and Jude still has his boat to take guests fishing if they want. Meals and transport can be arranged upon...More','$34','1 bedroom','1 bathroom','2 guests','1 night minimum','Neverbeen',NULL,NULL,'7.255108','79.84155','https://www.tripadvisor.com//VacationRentalReview-g2269230-d9559555-Jude_s_Home-Kochchikade_Negombo_Western_Province.html'),(3,548,'Hotel Dorset',NULL,'Hotel Dorset, situated on the golden sands of laidback Negombo is a peaceful retreat that offers warm, welcome and convenient facilities for leisure travellers. The property by the magnificent Indian Ocean offers genuine Sri Lankan hospitality while blending perfectly into Negombo island life. Conveniently located in close proximity to the city of Negombo, Hotel Dorset is a mere 10 km (20 minutes drive) from the Colombo International Airport, while Colombo is just a 36 km drive away.\n\nTourist License / Licencia de turismo N °: 2874 v...More','$40','15 bedrooms','15 bathrooms','35 guests','1 night minimum','Don G',NULL,NULL,'7.234719','79.84201','https://www.tripadvisor.com//VacationRentalReview-g297897-d11600948-Hotel_Dorset-Negombo_Western_Province.html'),(4,548,'infinity beach heaven',NULL,'Infinity Beach Heaven is the only privately managed guest-house right in front of the \'MORA WALA\' the world famouse only natural-beach-pool in Sri Lanka. The property is dreamed, drafted, designed, created and managed by two big hearts from Denmark & Sri Lanka. Entrance to the beach pool you will feel a professionally created bunch of true Sri Lankan hospitalities. Peaceful location, clean and comfy rooms, fine dining, private beach and different experience create you an amazing atmosphere to chill under the friendly sun and on the sandy beach of Negombo. B.B.Q Pit, Music, Water Sport, and any tour arrangement to any destination in the Island is on offer as per your choice. Come... try just one time the Infinity Beach Heaven.... you will be a reapeated friend of Negombo.....More','$103','3 bedrooms','3 bathrooms','7 guests','1 night minimum','nimal s',NULL,NULL,'7.202741','79.81822','https://www.tripadvisor.com//VacationRentalReview-g297897-d11720645-Infinity_beach_heaven-Negombo_Western_Province.html'),(5,517,'\'Mango\' The Transit Home',NULL,'Very convenient location, Just 3km to the airport. Super Markets, Food outlets, Restaurants, Nigh Clubs, Bus Stop, Train Station are in just walk in distance therefore no need to pay extra. Its very easy to travel to Colombo or Negambo since my place is next to Colombo- Negambo main road. Just 15 minutes to Negambo and 20 minutes to Colombo on express way. Public transport available 24X7. Best place for your first few days and last few days in Sri Lanka.\n\nRoom is reasonably cool with fans, depends on the season however if you want air conditioning, please request prior (for extra charge)\n\nFree Wifi available. Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner can be arranged upon requests (for extra charge). Pickup and Drop or transport can be arranged upon request (for extra charge).\n\nMy place is close to the airp...More','$18','1 bedroom','1 bathroom','2 guests','1 night minimum','Pemila G',NULL,NULL,'7.143479','79.87495','https://www.tripadvisor.com//VacationRentalReview-g1500185-d11956058-Mango_The_Transit_Home-Katunayake_Negombo_Western_Province.html'),(6,517,'ELZANGI BUDGET',NULL,'ELZANGI is managed by a family of Three Kids. We started up this as our hobby .With the help of this we use to meet people and share the knowledge and experience with them. And our children use to learn other cultures...\n\nWe started up this with two rooms ,now ELZANGI has expanded to 6 Rooms,and we have all the facilities for Families,couples and Single stays,that includes A/C and NON A/C rooms and apartments.\nWe have another project in remote village, that you will be loving to visit.\n\nELZANGI provides free Airport shuttle service for your convenience .\n\n\nTourist License / Licencia de turismo N °: PV 120700...More','$23','2 bedrooms','1 bathroom','7 guests','1 night minimum','ishanka j',NULL,NULL,'7.159984','79.87028','https://www.tripadvisor.com//VacationRentalReview-g1500185-d15628338-ELZANGI_BUDGET-Katunayake_Negombo_Western_Province.html');
